headline: Smart Mobility Powers Dual Circulation
summary: China's intelligent vehicle industry is embracing global cooperation with openness and innovation, while international automakers reevaluate the strategic importance of the Chinese market. Crucially, China's auto industry needs stronger connections to the world and deeper integration through global collaboration.

headline: Wall Street strategist explains how to navigate an ’AI Bubble’
summary: Investing.com -- The latest Sevens Report on Friday warned that a divergence between AI chipmakers and the broader equity market may be signaling early risks of an “AI bubble,” advising investors to monitor the semiconductor sector for signs of a market peak.
